TI  - STRUCTURE AND REGENERATION OF CANOPY SPECIES IN AN OLD-GROWTH EVERGREEN BROAD-LEAVED FOREST IN AYA DISTRICT, SOUTHWESTERN JAPAN
T2  - VEGETATIO
LA  - English
KW  - AYA
KW  - EVERGREEN BROAD-LEAVED FOREST
KW  - GAP FORMATION
KW  - REGENERATION PROBABILITY
