TI  - Post-landslide soil and vegetation recovery in a dry, montane system is slow and patchy
T2  - ECOSPHERE
LA  - English
KW  - disturbance
KW  - forest change
KW  - hillslope stabilization
KW  - landslide
KW  - mass movement
KW  - succession
