TI  - Vegetation succession on landslides in Hong Kong: Plant regeneration, survivorship and constraints to restoration
T2  - GLOBAL ECOLOGY AND CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - RAIN-FOREST
KW  - NATURAL REGENERATION
