TI  - Impacts of <i>Coriaria nepalensis</i> colonization on vegetation structure and regeneration dynamics in a mixed conifer forest of Indian Central Himalaya
T2  - JOURNAL OF FORESTRY RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Basal area
