TI  - Decadal vegetation succession from MODIS reveals the spatio-temporal evolution of post-seismic landsliding after the 2008 Wenchuan earthquake
T2  - REMOTE SENSING OF ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Post-seismic landslides
KW  - Vegetation recovery
KW  - Landscape evolution
KW  - Wenchuan earthquake
KW  - DEBRIS FLOWS
KW  - RECOVERY
