TI  - Slopewash, surface runoff and fine-litter transport in forest and landslide scars in humid-tropical steeplands, Luquillo Experimental Forest, Puerto Rico
T2  - EARTH SURFACE PROCESSES AND LANDFORMS
LA  - English
KW  - slopewash
