TI  - Comparison of RGB and Multispectral Unmanned Aerial Vehicle for Monitoring Vegetation Coverage Changes on a Landslide Area
T2  - DRONES
LA  - English
KW  - landslides
KW  - unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV)
KW  - multispectral
KW  - RGB
