TI  - Long-term impacts of forest disturbances: Comparing cumulative effects of clearcut logging versus landslide on stream conditions and abundance of a headwater stonefly <i>Scopura montana</i>
T2  - FRESHWATER BIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - canopy closure
KW  - forest succession
