TI  - Subtropical dendroecology - dating disturbances and forest dynamics in northwestern Argentina montane ecosystems
T2  - FOREST ECOLOGY AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Alnus acuminata
KW  - dendroecology
KW  - disturbances
