TI  - Investigation and numerical simulation of the 22 February 2018 landslide-triggered long-traveling debris flow at Pasir Panjang Village, Brebes Regency of Central Java, Indonesia
T2  - LANDSLIDES
LA  - English
KW  - Antecedent rainfall
KW  - Steep slope
KW  - Entrainment process
