TI  - Dynamic assessment of slope stability based on multi-source monitoring data and ensemble learning approaches: A case study of Jiuxianping landslide
T2  - GEOLOGICAL JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - slope stability
KW  - factor of safety (FS)
KW  - cross-validation (CV)
KW  - stacking ensemble learning
KW  - successive halving (SH)
KW  - RISK-ASSESSMENT
KW  - PREDICTION
KW  - MECHANISM
KW  - RESERVOIR
