TI  - Trade-offs between environmental and economic factors in conversion from exotic pine production to natural regeneration on erosion prone land
T2  - NEW ZEALAND JOURNAL OF FORESTRY SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Biophysical tree modelling
KW  - cost-benefit modelling
KW  - erosion susceptibility
