TI  - GEOMORPHOLOGY, DISTURBANCE, AND THE SOIL AND VEGETATION OF 2 SUBTROPICAL WET STEEPLAND WATERSHEDS OF PUERTO-RICO
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGY
LA  - English
