TI  - Altitude and landslide scale regulated the assembly of grassland communities on landslides during the recovery process after the magnitude 8.0 Wenchuan earthquake, China
T2  - ECOLOGICAL ENGINEERING
LA  - English
KW  - Earthquake
KW  - Community assembly
KW  - Niche-based hypothesis
KW  - Environmental filtering
