TI  - Radial increment in European spruce (<i>Picea abies</i>) as indicator of sanitary condition of spruce forests in the Ukrainian Carpathians
T2  - BIOSYSTEMS DIVERSITY
LA  - English
KW  - individual growth ring chronologies
KW  - generalized growth ring chronologies
KW  - index of radial increment
KW  - increment of abnormality of radial increment
KW  - cycles of radial increment
KW  - NORWAY SPRUCE
KW  - GROWTH-PATTERNS
KW  - L. KARST.
