FX  - This review and the related research have been developed within the interdisciplinary project ERODYN (Shallow erosion dynamics in mountain grasslands of South Tyrol: Monitoring, process analysis and mitigation measures; http://www.mountainresearch.at/erodyn/), which is funded by the Autonomous Province of Bozen - South Tyrol (Italy) with grant B76J17000380003. Further, the Free University of Bozen-Bolzano funded this research. We also thank the Austrian Federal Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry, Environment and Water Management (BMLFUW) for funding the EROSTAB project. Finally, we would like to thank the Federal State of Tyrol (Austria) for providing digital terrain models and orthophotos. We declare no conflict of interests.
