TI  - Morphoevolution of the Seymareh landslide-dam lake system (Zagros Mountains, Iran): Implications for Holocene climate and environmental changes
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Landslide dam
KW  - Lake overflow
