TI  - Changes in spatial point patterns of pioneer woody plants across a large tropical landslide
T2  - ACTA OECOLOGICA-INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Stress-gradient hypothesis
KW  - Negative and positive interactions
KW  - Disturbances
KW  - Pair-correlation function
KW  - Random labelling
KW  - Independence
