TI  - Anti-erosion rehabilitation: Effects of revegetation method and site traits on introduced and native plant cover and richness
T2  - SCIENCE OF THE TOTAL ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Erosion control
KW  - Landslide
KW  - Quarry
KW  - Restoration
