TI  - Structural traits of woody plants and geomorphological conditions to the vegetation recovery at Ksudach caldera (Southern Kamchatka) since the explosive eruption in 1907
T2  - JOURNAL OF MOUNTAIN SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Ksudach caldera
KW  - Pioneer species
KW  - Woody plants
