TI  - Hydromechanical triggering of landslides: From progressive local failures to mass release
T2  - WATER RESOURCES RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - SELF-ORGANIZED-CRITICALITY
KW  - SLOPE STABILITY ANALYSIS
KW  - SHALLOW LANDSLIDES
KW  - SHEAR-STRENGTH
