TI  - New evidence for a major late Quaternary submarine landslide on the external western levee of Laurentian Fan
T2  - SUBAQUEOUS MASS MOVEMENTS AND THEIR CONSEQUENCES: ASSESSING GEOHAZARDS, ENVIRONMENTAL IMPLICATIONS AND ECONOMIC SIGNIFICANCE OF SUBAQUEOUS LANDSLIDES
LA  - English
KW  - CONTINENTAL-MARGIN
