TI  - Land use mapping and its relation to mass wasting and gullying in North-Western Rif (Morocco)
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGIE-RELIEF PROCESSUS ENVIRONNEMENT
LA  - French
KW  - land use
KW  - mapping
KW  - mass wasting
KW  - badlands
KW  - Chefchaouen
