TI  - Multiple stable equilibria in grasslands mediated by herbivore population dynamics and foraging behavior
T2  - ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - alternate stable states
KW  - disturbance
KW  - foraging
KW  - grasslands
KW  - herbivory
KW  - herbivore population dynamics
