TI  - Anthropogenic processes, natural hazards, and interactions in a multi-hazard framework
T2  - EARTH-SCIENCE REVIEWS
LA  - English
KW  - LANDSLIDE SUSCEPTIBILITY
KW  - RISK-ASSESSMENT
KW  - IMPACT
KW  - DEFORESTATION
