TI  - Deforestation and its geomorphic impact triggered by historic iron-ore production at the Styrian Erzberg
T2  - MITTEILUNGEN DER OSTERREICHISCHEN GEOGRAPHISCHEN GESELLSCHAFT
LA  - German
KW  - BRITISH-COLUMBIA
KW  - SOIL-EROSION
