TI  - Palaeoenvironment of the Eocene Eckfeld Maar lake (Germany):: implications from geochemical analysis of the oil shale sequence
T2  - ORGANIC GEOCHEMISTRY
LA  - English
KW  - CARBON ISOTOPIC COMPOSITION
KW  - ORGANIC-MATTER
