TI  - Economic evaluation of ecological restoration options in gypsum habitats after mining
T2  - JOURNAL FOR NATURE CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - Habitat recovery
KW  - Quarrying
KW  - Priority-habitat conservation
KW  - Gypsophiles
KW  - Restoration activities
