TI  - Engineering geology and subsidence mechanism of a mountain surface in the Daliang Lead-zinc Ore Mine in China
T2  - BULLETIN OF ENGINEERING GEOLOGY AND THE ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Mining engineering
KW  - Geological disaster
KW  - Mountain collapse
