TI  - Monitoring of avulsion channel evolution and river morphology changes using UAV photogrammetry: Case study of the gravel bed Ondava River in Outer Western Carpathians
T2  - AREA
LA  - English
KW  - avulsion channel
KW  - channel changes
KW  - chute cutoff
KW  - UAV technology
