TI  - Long-term distribution and habitat changes of protected wildlife: giant pandas in Wolong Nature Reserve, China
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND POLLUTION RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Giant panda
KW  - Space use
